yasmāt kleśotpādān na svātantryādidam etat parasparaviruddhacaritam eṣāṃ bālānām iti matvā.

<commentary>ātmasattvavaśaṃ svaparāyattaṃ sarvakālam. kiṃ sarvatra? na. anavadyeṣu vastuṣūbhayasāvadyaśūnyeṣu. kiṃvat? nirmāṇam iva nirmitavat. vigatamānaṃ mānasaṃ dhārayāmi. eṣo 'ham iti bodhisattvo manasi niveśayet.</commentary>

asmād api saṃvegamanasikārāc cittasyānarthavivarjanena rakṣā vidhātavyety āha. aticireṇa kālena labdham uktaṃ kṣaṇavaraṃ smaraṇena cetasi kṛtvā punaḥ punar antaraṃ sthirīkaromīdṛśam uktasvabhāvam.
